{"tid":2217038,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港共無論如何都唔會阻止持有BNO港人出境","createTime":"2020-09-25T07:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T10:52:03.000Z","uid":77625,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f9eb7debca3667ef8aef2f46c229b3aa3359f90a","tid":2217038,"uid":77625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:12:07.000Z","msg":"有一種說法話林鄭無可能阻止BNO港人出境移民，因為如果佢咁做就係攬炒香港經濟，同埋香港人可以去其他國家再轉機英國。俾大家睇下祖國既例子，就知香港既未來<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">1. 集中護照管理，不愛國不能出境</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2776321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2776321&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzg2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=19f976f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2776321&h=4f0122cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2776321</a><br />\n中國雜誌《寒冬》報導，當局會對申請出國的人進行審查，必須符合「政治可靠」、「歷史清楚」、「熱愛社會主義祖國」等條件，再來著重審查個人狀況，及其家庭成員的情況。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寧夏回族自治區中有家醫院，更是收到<strong><ins><span class=\"red\">要求交出所有員工護照</span></ins></strong>，由警方逐一比對所有人的護照簽發時間，一一收繳，雖然有許多員工反對，但員工說：「你不想交都不行，否則人家就直接找你，<strong><ins><span class=\"red\">把你帶到公安局去</span></ins></strong>，嚇得我和同事趕緊把護照上交了。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">2. 借疫情為名，無限期限制出境 </span></strong></span><br />\n你以為黑警用599G玩肺炎玩到出神入化?玩到最勁可以唔俾你出境<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例子:今年7月去唔到柬埔寨<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.soundofhope.org/post/405520?lang=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F405520%3Flang%3Db5&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzg2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=8a976d61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundofhope.org/post/405520?lang=b5</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">3.特區政府公務員、醫生、老師、中資員工高危</span></span></strong><br />\n7月1日起，中共《公職人員政務處分法》開始生效，<strong><ins><span class=\"red\">嚴控6類在職公職人員出境、取得外國國籍</span></ins></strong>或綠卡<br />\n此前已有消息指，<span class=\"red\">公務員、醫生、教師、國企</span>員工等被要求上交護照，由單位統一管理，顯示中共當局日益收緊對公民出境的限制。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲係武漢試行︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2020/07/31/941470.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2020%2F07%2F31%2F941470.html&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzg2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=7744b09b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2020/07/31/941470.html</a><br />\n武漢武漢公安出入境管理局網站近日發布通知稱：根據《關於開展違規辦理和持有因私出國（境）證件專項清理行動的通知》（武組監〔2020〕15號）文件要求，持有效因私出國（境）證件未遺失或毀損的所有在武漢國家機關、國有控股企業、事業單位、部隊等單位人員，<span class=\"red\"><strong><ins>應將因私護照上交，由單位組織（人事）部門集中收存保管</ins></strong></span>，如果不交的話，就會被註銷。<br />\n百度一下，會搵到更多例子，原來早幾年已經做緊野，keyword&quot;因私出境申请&quot; (出國都要申請?!)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinalawedu.com/web/208/wq1503306733.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinalawedu.com%2Fweb%2F208%2Fwq1503306733.shtml&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8Qfwzg2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=15683e3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinalawedu.com/web/208/wq1503306733.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">4. 為左唔俾錢流出去中國，限制旅遊措施又唔係未做過</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Yy_SyMBNBGT0QCbk9E5Ryy6Gn38=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6RJNI3XTXVHR3EVCGXF63RJ56M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYy_SyMBNBGT0QCbk9E5Ryy6Gn38%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6RJNI3XTXVHR3EVCGXF63RJ56M.jpg&h=765dee85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突發奇想，到底仲可以有咩招數?<br />\n1. 就算阻唔到你走，就唔俾你返黎，加大你離開成本 (到時搵籍口話你測試not qualify/不合理縮短72小時要求好難?)<br />\n全球新冠肺炎疫情持續，政府昨日（24日）刊憲將英國列入高危地區，要求由英國返港人士在登機前，須持有72小時內發出的核酸檢測陰性證明，到港後須到酒店檢疫，10月1日起生效 <br />\n<br />\n2. 唔俾你拎MPF (已經做緊)<br />\n<br />\n3. 要你放棄永久香港居民身份(建制吹緊)<br />\n<br />\n4. 西方國家(美、英、歐盟)制裁香港，中國反制唔俾中國(包括香港人)因私事去西方國家，經濟制裁西方國家 (一石二鳥，又可以滿足小粉紅心理內宣，又可以搞香港人)<br />\n<br />\n5. 台海小型衝突，搵籍口封鎖空域<br />\n<br />\n6.中國大規模亂發特區護照，逼到西方國家取消特區護照免簽證安排。唔好諗住拎BNO就得，雖然你出香港境係用身份證，但佢可以check你有無有效護照?(有咩做唔出?)<br />\n<br />\n7.因為同X個國家無引渡條例，所以政府為左怕有criminal走佬去外國，去無引渡協議既國家，出境要填申請書審批<br />\n<br />\n如果上面都搞唔到，大家唔記得?<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/5/54/Xinjiang_Re-education_Camp_Lop_County.jpg/220px-Xinjiang_Re-education_Camp_Lop_County.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F5%2F54%2FXinjiang_Re-education_Camp_Lop_County.jpg%2F220px-Xinjiang_Re-education_Camp_Lop_County.jpg&h=621aedb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2680000/2684510/20200_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2680000%2F2684510%2F20200_1024.png&h=d8ee99bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>你真係覺得港共會眼白白睇住你地班香港人賣樓走人?</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9d9d560071ca3a1dd86c39b7ba288a80920e8455","tid":2217038,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"定啦 冇得去外國退休班離地藍絲仲肉緊過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc9212caff7ee4dac89106066a6852c130fa580","tid":2217038,"uid":77625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d9d560071ca3a1dd86c39b7ba288a80920e8455","tid":2217038,"uid":14494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"定啦 冇得去外國退休班離地藍絲仲肉緊過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" cla